<doc id="18387" wikidata="Q10554048" url="?curid=18387" title="Lanista">
<text>Lanista is a genus of African bush-crickets (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae) in the subfamily Conocephalinae.

==Species==
* &quot;Lanista affinis&quot; Bolívar, 1906
* &quot;Lanista annulicornis&quot; (Walker, 1869)
* &quot;Lanista crassicollis&quot; Bolívar, 1906
* &quot;Lanista varelai&quot; Bolívar, 1906

